flowchart TD
    %% Base styling to ensure white background
    classDef default fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000;
    
    %% External Entities (Rectangles)
    Student[[Student]]
    Instructor[[Instructor]]
    Admin[[Admin]]
    SuperAdmin[[Super Admin]]

    %% Processes (Circles/Ovals)
    P1((1.0<br/>User<br/>Management))
    P2((2.0<br/>Course & Booking<br/>Management))
    P3((3.0<br/>Payment<br/>Processing))
    P4((4.0<br/>Training &<br/>Evaluation))
    P5((5.0<br/>Fleet<br/>Management))
    P6((6.0<br/>Financial & Admin<br/>Operations))

    %% Data Stores (Open-ended rectangles)
    D1[(D1: User DB)]
    D2[(D2: Course/Booking DB)]
    D3[(D3: Payment DB)]
    D4[(D4: Progress/Test DB)]
    D5[(D5: Fleet DB)]
    D6[(D6: Finance DB)]

    %% Interactions with 1.0 User Management
    Student -->|Registration info, Auth credentials| P1
    P1 -->|Auth status| Student
    Instructor -->|Auth credentials, Leaves| P1
    Admin -->|Manage Users/Leaves| P1
    P1 <-->|User Profiles, Leave requests| D1

    %% Interactions with 2.0 Course & Booking Management
    Student -->|Browse courses, Request slots| P2
    P2 -->|Schedule updates, Booking confirmation| Student
    Admin -->|Create courses, Manage slots, Waitlists| P2
    P2 -->|Assign schedule| Instructor
    P2 <-->|Course details, Timetables| D2

    %% Interactions with 3.0 Payment Processing
    Student -->|Fees, RC Renewal, Retest Payments| P3
    P3 -->|Payment Receipts, Application Status| Student
    Admin -->|Verify payments, Monitor RC/Retest| P3
    P3 <-->|Transaction Logs, Application details| D3

    %% Interactions with 4.0 Training & Evaluation
    Student -->|Mock Test answers| P4
    P4 -->|Test Results, Skill Progress updates| Student
    Instructor -->|Update Skill parameters, Trip Logs| P4
    Admin -->|Add Mock Test Questions| P4
    P4 <-->|Marks, Skill matrices, Questions| D4

    %% Interactions with 5.0 Fleet Management
    Instructor -->|Log Fuel, Log Maintenance| P5
    Admin -->|Add Vehicles, Track Logs| P5
    P5 <-->|Vehicle records, Expenses| D5

    %% Interactions with 6.0 Financial & Admin Operations
    Instructor -->|Mark Attendance| P6
    P6 -->|View Salary| Instructor
    Admin -->|Process Salary, Send Fund Request, Announcements| P6
    P6 -->|Fund Request Updates| Admin
    SuperAdmin -->|Review Fund Request, Analytics Query| P6
    P6 -->|Request Status| SuperAdmin
    P6 <-->|Revenue, Salaries, Expense Reports| D6
